    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes a Hybrid Hierarchical Multi-Domain Service Function Chaining (hhSFC) architecture that extends Service Function Chaining (SFC) to multiple domains with different technology, administration or ownership. The goals of Hybrid Hierarchical SFC are to reduce the complexity of the control plane in a multi-domain scene and make the negotiation between different domains possible.</t>
